						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">King: Tribhuvanachchakkravartigaḷ Rāja[rāja]dēva III Year 14: <hi rend="italic">Rishabha</hi>, śu. di. 10, Thursday, <hi rend="italic">Hastam</hi> = 23 May 1230 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records a gift of 1(3/4) <hi rend="italic">paḻaṅkāśu</hi> by a native of (village), Peruṅgaṉalvaṭṭam for burning a twilight lamp to the god at Tirunīrmalai. The priest of the temple, Śrī Kṛishṇa Bhaṭṭan received the gift and agreed to maintain the lamp perpetually.</p>						

